        "part_type": "Hadith",
        "path": "/books/al-amali-mufid:23:26:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/13/23/26/1",
        "text": [
          ": سمعت أبا عبد الله جعفر بن محمد صلوات الله عليهما يقول: إن العمل الصالح ليذهب إلى الجنة فيمهد لصاحبه كما يبعث الرجل غلامه فيفرش له. ثم قرأ: \" وأما الذين آمنوا وعملوا الصالحات فلأنفسهم يمهدون \" ."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.mulla-asgharali-m-m-jaffer": [
            "26. And with the first chain of narration, from ‘Ali ibn Mahzyar, from ‘Ali ibn al-Nu’man, from Dawood ibn Farqad, who said: I heard Abu Abdillah Ja’far ibn Muhammad, peace be upon both of them, say: \"Surely, the righteous deeds will go to the Paradise to prepare for theirs doers, the way a person sends his servant to furnish for him. Then he recited: ’And as for those who believe, and do righteous deeds, they prepare for their own souls’ (al-Rum, 30:44).\""
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
